videos.description: Kevin Love saves the ball from going out of bounds and it ends up with  Kyrie Irving, who finds LeBron James for the two-handed jam.

videos.description: With this layup in the third quarter, LeBron James passes Shaquille O'Neal for fourth place on the all-time playoff scoring list with 5,251 points.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (This layup gives LeBron fourth place on the postseason scoring list) 2016/05/19 ESHEET

videos.description: After beating the Raptors in Game 2 of the Eastern Conference finals, the Cavaliers show off some fancy handshakes

videos.description: Tim Legler says Kyle Lowry's lack of aggressiveness and confidence has a snowball effect on the rest of the team, causing the Raptors to fall in an 0-2 hole in the Eastern Conference finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Legler: Lowry not playing with any confidence) 2016/05/19 SC

videos.headline: Legler: Lowry not playing with any confidence

videos.description: After beating the Raptors in Game 2 of the Eastern Conference finals, the Cavaliers walk back to the locker room while J.R. Smith holds a toddler and LeBron James is greeted by Kareem Abdul-Jabbar.
